0:26:34.704,000 --> 0:26:36,000
is when you have something that's non-economic

494
0:26:36.894,000 --> 0:26:37,000
and you're trying to fund that --

495
0:26:38.537,000 --> 0:26:39,000
that, to me, mostly is a waste.

496
0:26:40.489,000 --> 0:26:41,000
Unless you're very close,

497
0:26:42.06,000 --> 0:26:45,000
